%I A390122 #24 Mar 27 2026 18:11:57
%S A390122 0,1,4,44,1899,267976,112877832
%N A390122 Number of directed cycles in the n X n grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A390122 Excludes 0 length cycles; including them increases each term by 1.
%C A390122 Number of undirected cycles gives A394067. Number of directed cycles not reduced for symmetry gives A140517*2.
%e A390122 a(3) = 4 (all symmetric and count as 1 each both undirected and directed):
%e A390122   +>>+>>+    +  +  +    +  +  +    +>>+>>+
%e A390122   ^     v                          ^     v
%e A390122   +  +  +    +>>+>>+    +  +>>+    +<<+  +
%e A390122   ^     v    ^     v       ^  v       ^  v
%e A390122   +<<+<<+    +<<+<<+    +  +<<+    +  +<<+.
%e A390122 Nonsymmetric cycles count as 2 each when directed, e.g.:
%e A390122   +  +--+--+      +  +>>+>>+       +  +<<+<<+
%e A390122      |     |         ^     v          v     ^
%e A390122   +  +--+  +      +  +<<+  +       +  +>>+  +
%e A390122         |  |  ->        ^  v  and        v  ^
%e A390122   +  +  +  +      +  +  +  +       +  +  +  +
%e A390122         |  |            ^  v             v  ^
%e A390122   +  +  +--+      +  +  +<<+       +  +  +>>+.
%o A390122 (PARI) \\ See Hohn link in A394065.
%Y A390122 Cf. A394067, A140517.
%K A390122 nonn,more,new
%O A390122 1,3
%A A390122 _Charles L. Hohn_, Mar 22 2026
